\c 48
\s Ukwabiwa kwelizwe
\p
\v 1 La-ke ngamabizo ezizwe\x + 48.23; 45.8.\x*. Kusukela ekucineni kwasenyakatho\x + 47.15,16,17.\x*, kuze kube seceleni\x + 2 Sam. 18.4; Josh. 15.46.\x* kwendlela yeHethiloni\x + 47.15,16,17.\x*, ekungeneni kweHamathi\x + 47.15,16,17.\x*, iHazari-Enani\x + 47.15,16,17.\x*, umngcele weDamaseko\x + 47.15,16,17.\x* ngasenyakatho, kuze kube seceleni\x + 2 Sam. 18.4; Josh. 15.46.\x* kweHamathi\x + 47.15,16,17.\x*; ngoba \add lezi\add* zinhlangothi zakhe empumalanga \add l\add*entshonalanga, \add isabelo\add* esisodwa \add sika\add*Dani\x + Nani 2.25-31.\x*.
\v 2 Langasemngceleni kaDani, kusukela ehlangothini lwempumalanga kusiya ehlangothini lwentshonalanga, \add isabelo\add* esisodwa \add sika\add*Asheri\x + Nani 2.25-31.\x*.
\v 3 Langasemngceleni kaAsheri, kusukela ehlangothini lwempumalanga kusiya ehlangothini lwentshonalanga, \add isabelo\add* esisodwa \add sika\add*Nafithali\x + Nani 2.25-31.\x*.
\v 4 Langasemngceleni kaNafithali, kusukela ehlangothini lwempumalanga kusiya ehlangothini lwentshonalanga, \add isabelo\add* esisodwa \add sika\add*Manase\x + 47.13.\x*.
\v 5 Langasemngceleni kaManase, kusukela ehlangothini lwempumalanga kusiya ehlangothini lwentshonalanga, \add isabelo\add* esisodwa \add sika\add*Efrayimi\x + 47.13.\x*.
\v 6 Langasemngceleni kaEfrayimi, kusukela ehlangothini lwempumalanga kusiya ehlangothini lwentshonalanga, \add isabelo\add* esisodwa \add sika\add*Rubeni.
\v 7 Langasemngceleni kaRubeni, kusukela ehlangothini lwempumalanga kusiya ehlangothini lwentshonalanga, \add isabelo\add* esisodwa \add sika\add*Juda.
\p
\v 8 Langasemngceleni kaJuda, kusukela ehlangothini lwempumalanga kusiya ehlangothini lwentshonalanga, kuzakuba ngumnikelo elizawunikela\x + 45.1-6.\x*, ububanzi buzakuba zinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu, lobude njengesinye sezabelo, kusukela ehlangothini lwempumalanga kuze kube sehlangothini lwentshonalanga; njalo indawo engcwele izakuba phakathi kwaso\x + 48.10,21.\x*.
\v 9 Umnikelo elizawunikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 45.1-6.\x* uzakuba yibude obuyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu, lobubanzi bezinkulungwane ezilitshumi.
\v 10 Njalo kuzakuba kuso umnikelo ongcwele wabapristi\x + 45.1-6.\x*, ngenyakatho izinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu, langentshonalanga ububanzi obuyizinkulungwane ezilitshumi, langempumalanga ububanzi obuyizinkulungwane ezilitshumi, langeningizimu ubude obuyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu; njalo indawo engcwele yeN\nd kosi\x + 48.10,21.\x*\nd* izakuba phakathi kwaso.
\v 11 Sizakuba ngesabapristi abangcwelisiweyo\x + 45.1-6.\x*\x + 44.15.\x* bamadodana kaZadoki\x + 40.46.\x*, abagcine umlindo wami\x + 40.45.\x*, abangaduhanga lapho abantwana bakoIsrayeli beduha\x + 44.10,15.\x*, njengalokho amaLevi aduha\x + 44.10,15.\x*.
\v 12 Lokunikelweyo komnikelo welizwe\x + 45.1-6.\x* kuzakuba kubo yinto engcwelengcwele ngasemngceleni wamaLevi.
\v 13 Njalo maqondana lomngcele wabapristi\x + 45.5.\x*, amaLevi azakuba lobude bezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu, lobubanzi bezinkulungwane ezilitshumi. Ubude bonke buzakuba zinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu, lobubanzi bube zinkulungwane ezilitshumi.
\v 14 Njalo kabayikuthengisa okwakho\x + Levi 27.10,28,33.\x*, kabayikuntshintshisa\x + Levi 27.10,28,33.\x*, kabayikudlulisa\x + Nani 27.7,8.\x* izithelo zakuqala zelizwe\x + 44.30.\x*, ngoba kungcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\p
\v 15 Lezinkulungwane ezinhlanu eziseleyo\x + 45.6.\x* ebubanzini maqondana lezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu, zizakuba ngezingengcwele zomuzi\x + 42.20.\x*, ezokuhlala, lezamadlelo\x + 45.6.\x*; lomuzi uzakuba phakathi kwazo.
\v 16 Lalezi zizakuba yizilinganiso zaso; uhlangothi lwenyakatho luzakuba zinkulungwane ezine lamakhulu amahlanu\x + 48.30,32-34; Isam. 21.16; Hez. 48.20.\x*, lohlangothi lweningizimu izinkulungwane ezine lamakhulu amahlanu\x + 48.30,32-34; Isam. 21.16; Hez. 48.20.\x*, lehlangothini lwempumalanga izinkulungwane ezine lamakhulu amahlanu\x + 48.30,32-34; Isam. 21.16; Hez. 48.20.\x*, lohlangothi lwentshonalanga izinkulungwane ezine lamakhulu amahlanu\x + 48.30,32-34; Isam. 21.16; Hez. 48.20.\x*.
\v 17 Njalo amadlelo omuzi\x + 48.17; 45.2.\x* azakuba ngamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amahlanu ngasenyakatho, lamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amahlanu ngaseningizimu, lamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amahlanu ngasempumalanga, lamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amahlanu ngasentshonalanga.
\v 18 Lokuseleyo ngobude maqondana lomnikelo ongcwele kuzakuba zinkulungwane ezilitshumi ngempumalanga, lezinkulungwane ezilitshumi ngentshonalanga; njalo kuzakuba maqondana lomnikelo ongcwele\x + 45.6.\x*. Lenzuzo yakho izakuba yikudla kwezisebenzi zomuzi\x + 48.19; 36.9,34.\x*.
\v 19 Njalo izisebenzi zomuzi\x + 48.19; 36.9,34.\x* zizawusebenzela zivela kuzo zonke izizwe zakoIsrayeli\x + 45.6.\x*.
\v 20 Wonke umnikelo\x + 48.21.\x* uzakuba zinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu, lezinkungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu. Lizanikela umnikelo ongcwele ulingane inhlangothi zozine, kanye lelifa lomuzi\x + 40.47.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Njalo okuseleyo kuzakuba ngokwesiphathamandla\x + 45.7.\x*, ngapha langapha komnikelo ongcwele, lokwenzuzo yomuzi, ngaphambi kwezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu zomnikelo, kuze kube semngceleni wempumalanga\x + 48.21.\x* lentshonalanga, ngaphambi kwezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lanhlanu, ngasemngceleni wentshonalanga, maqondana lezigaba zeziphathamandla; lomnikelo ongcwele lendawo engcwele yendlu kuzakuba phakathi kwakho\x + 10,21.\x*.
\v 22 Futhi kusukela enzuzweni yamaLevi, lakusukela enzuzweni yomuzi, ephakathi kokungokwesiphathamandla, phakathi komngcele kaJuda lomngcele kaBhenjamini, kuzakuba ngokwesiphathamandla.
\v 23 Mayelana lokuseleyo kwezizwe\x + 48.23; 45.8.\x*, kusukela kuhlangothi lwempumalanga kusiya kuhlangothi lwentshonalanga, uBhenjamini uzakuba l\add esabelo\add* esisodwa.
\v 24 Lasemngceleni wakoBhenjamini, kusukela kuhlangothi lwempumalanga kusiya kuhlangothi lwentshonalanga, uSimeyoni uzakuba lesisodwa.
\v 25 Lasemngceleni kaSimeyoni, kusukela kuhlangothi lwempumalanga kusiya kuhlangothi lwentshonalanga, uIsakari uzakuba lesisodwa.
\v 26 Lasemngceleni kaIsakari, kusukela kuhlangothi lwempumalanga kusiya kuhlangothi lwentshonalanga, uZebuluni uzakuba lesisodwa.
\v 27 Lasemngceleni kaZebuluni, kusukela kuhlangothi lwempumalanga kusiya kuhlangothi lwentshonalanga, uGadi uzakuba lesisodwa.
\v 28 Lasemngceleni kaGadi, kuhlangothi lweningizimu ngaseningizimu\x + 47.19.\x*, umngcele uzasuka eTamari \add kuze kube se\add*manzi\add ni\add* eMeribathi-Kadeshi\x + 47.19.\x*, kuze kube semfuleni, kuze kube selwandle olukhulu\x + 47.19.\x*.
\v 29 Yilo ilizwe elizalaba ngenkatho\x + 47.22; 47.14.\x* libe yilifa kuzo izizwe zakoIsrayeli, njalo lezi yizabelo zazo, itsho iNkosi uJehova.
\s Amasango eJerusalema
\p
\v 30 Lalokhu yikuphuma komuzi\x + Nani 34.4,5,8,9,12; Josh. 15.4,7,11.\x* kuvela ehlangothini lwenyakatho\x + 48.30,32-34; Isam. 21.16; Hez. 48.20.\x*, izilinganiso ezizinkulungwane ezine lamakhulu amahlanu\x + 48.30,32-34; Isam. 21.16; Hez. 48.20.\x*.
\v 31 Njalo amasango omuzi azakuba ngamabizo ezizwe zakoIsrayeli\x + Isam. 21.12,13.\x*; amasango amathathu ngasenyakatho; isango elilodwa\x + Dute. 33.6-8.\x* elikaRubeni\x + Isam. 21.12,13.\x*, isango elilodwa elikaJuda\x + Isam. 21.12,13.\x*, isango elilodwa elikaLevi\x + Isam. 21.12,13.\x*.
\v 32 Lehlangothini lwempumalanga izinkulungwane ezine lamakhulu amahlanu\x + 48.30,32-34; Isam. 21.16; 48.20.\x*, lamasango amathathu; ngitsho isango elilodwa elikaJosefa, isango elilodwa elikaBhenjamini, isango elilodwa elikaDani.
\v 33 Lehlangothini lweningizimu izilinganiso ezizinkulungwane ezine lamakhulu amahlanu\x + 48.30,32-34; Isam. 21.16; 48.20.\x*, lamasango amathathu; isango elilodwa elikaSimeyoni, isango elilodwa elikaIsakari, isango elilodwa elikaZebuluni.
\v 34 Uhlangothi lwentshonalanga, izinkulungwane ezine lamakhulu amahlanu\x + 48.30,32-34; Isam. 21.16; 48.20.\x*, amasango azo amathathu; isango elilodwa elikaGadi, isango elilodwa elikaAsheri, isango elilodwa elikaNafithali.
\v 35 Inhlangothi zonke yizinkulungwane ezilitshumi lesificaminwembili. Njalo ibizo lomuzi kusukela nga\add lolo\add*suku lizakuba\x + Isa. 60.14. Jer. 33.16.\x*: IN\nd kosi\nd* ilapha\x + 35.10; Jer. 3.17; Jow. 3.21; Zek. 2.10; Isam.21.3.\x*.